subject: systemd: disable isf-panel.service
commitMessage:
systemd: disable isf-panel.service

If this service is enabled, scim-launcher does not launch the virtual
keyboard, as it is designed to fork/exec isf-panel-efl itself and not
use an already-existing service.

Disabling the user session service fixes the issue.

Change-Id: Ieb01a1bed890a2a22a0578a50041b409c2c81b31
Signed-off-by: Patrick McCarty <patrick.mccarty@linux.intel.com>
